  "story": "A triumphant Easter bhajan celebrating Christ's victory over death and the grave. This traditional Hindi resurrection hymn fills churches with joy on Easter Sunday morning. Its victorious melody and confident lyrics proclaim the central truth of the Christian faith — that Jesus is alive and death has been conquered forever.",
  "lyrics": {
